{"tid":1953922,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連拿曾出現武漢肺炎病徵：試過缺氧25分鐘唞唔到氣","createTime":"2020-04-01T12:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T04:55:51.000Z","uid":70063,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"91b0129c4e2db40e90f911f2a8d969c0e720ad7f","tid":1953922,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"目前由AC米蘭外借至阿士東維拉的西班牙門將連拿，3月初曾出現武漢肺炎病徵，但自己沒有進行病毒檢測，目前情況已正在好轉，他講述病發時曾無法呼吸，是他人生最恐懼的時刻。<br />\n<br />\n這位37歲的西班牙門將表示：「從我出現症狀以來，我就肯定自己感染了武漢肺炎。發燒、乾咳、持續的頭痛和容易疲勞我都有過。」<br />\n<br />\n他續指：「讓我最害怕是缺氧的時候，我曾在一段時間無法好好呼吸，缺氧接近25分鐘，當時是我人生最糟糕的日子。我在自己的房間待了8天，因為我希望和我五位小孩和兩位老人家保持距離。幸好我現在已戰勝了它。」<br />\n<br />\n對於英超停擺，他表示：「球季能否完成並不重要，健康必須要是首要考慮，每個人的幸福和健康都應在足球之上。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200401/D5WKCBOI3O6CDRJLZWRAJPBWHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200401%2FD5WKCBOI3O6CDRJLZWRAJPBWHM%2F&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=ec287227\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200401%2FD5WKCBOI3O6CDRJLZWRAJPBWHM%2F&h=1d691632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200401/D5WKCBOI3O6CDRJLZWRAJPBWHM/</a>"},{"pid":"e6ea4bf319e67d2908276db612b61cfb0eed39d1","tid":1953922,"uid":41524,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:02:47.000Z","msg":"連拿最出名就係戇鳩"},{"pid":"ce42ee45e21f1193579841b429b87c9038c20d77","tid":1953922,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6ea4bf319e67d2908276db612b61cfb0eed39d1","tid":1953922,"uid":41524,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:02:47.000Z","msg":"連拿最出名就係戇鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"拉爾拿先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c60e3f6a94df1fddfee2e42a918965887f1f0ce","tid":1953922,"uid":34571,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16: